==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Porousness
<hw>Por"ous*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality of
being porous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The open parts; the interstices of anything.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They will forcibly get into the <qex>porousness</qex> of it.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir K. Digby.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Porpentine</ent>⟦br⟧
